<DOCNO> LA022189-0027 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 21281 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 21, 1989, Tuesday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part 2; Page 1; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
