<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 La Jolla-based Agouron Pharmaceuticals reported a net loss of $1.1 million for 
the second quarter ended Dec. 31, compared to a $742,000 net loss the previous 
second quarter. Revenue rose to $530,000, up from $$173,600 during the like 
quarter a year ago. 
</P>
<P>
Agouron reported a $1.9-million net loss for the six-month period ended Dec. 
31, compared to a $1.3-million net loss a year earlier. Revenue rose to $1.1 
million, up from $345,200 a year ago. 
</P>
</TEXT>
