<HEADLINE>
<P>
SADDLEBACK DEFEATS GLENDALE IN BASEBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Saddleback College defeated Glendale, 9-4, in a nonconference baseball game 
Monday afternoon at Saddleback. 
</P>
<P>
Tony Spaan led the Saddleback hitting attack with two hits, including a home 
run in the third inning. Larry Maddux also had a home run for Saddleback (4-1). 
</P>
</TEXT>
