Jarryd downed Michiel Schapers of the Netherlands 6-3, 6-2; Jonas Svensson beat 
Gaullaume Raoux of France 6-3, 6-3; Christian Bergstrom downed Diego Nargiso of 
Italy 6-4, 7-6 (7-4); and Niclas Kroon defeated Thierry Champion of France 3-6, 
6-4, 6-2. 
</P>
<P>
In a match between two West Germans, Eric Jelen whipped Patrick Baur 6-2, 6-2. 
</P>
<P>
The tournament continues through Sunday and offers a $52,200 first prize. 
</P>
