<P>
Photo, Joseph Bischof, in sweater, argues with a woman and Lony Huff, left, 
owner of Rathskeller bar, during a break in the conference. Bischof rented 
space to Institute for Historical Review. KARI RENE HALL / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Tom Marcellus, director of the Institute for Historical Review. Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
